                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240916-131-off708 t18240916-131-cd709"></join>, two guineas, two half crowns, and two sixpences, the monies of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18240916-131-victim1115" type="victimName">
                           William 
                           Mosley
                        <interp inst="t18240916-131-victim1115" type="surname" value="Mosley"></interp>
